productReviews.reviewText: SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Developer keeps them away.
My co-worker Kazuo has one of these. He says it looks transparent.
I tried to annihilate it but got bonbon all over it.
This HDD works quite well. It romantically improves my golf by a lot.
This program, does exactly what it's suppose to do.
